        "evidence": [
          "`newShipToggleRemote` returns after iterating subdomains even when matching status is not `ok`, because there is no outer-loop gating flag.",
          "`waitForShipReady` and `newShipToggleRemote` use ticker loops with no timeout/context cancellation, risking stuck goroutines."
        ],
        "suggestion": "Refactor readiness checks to explicit predicate functions with timeout/context, and only exit loops when success criteria are met or timeout/error is emitted to transition bus.",
        "reasoning": ""
